# Rules

1. `.cursor/rules/architecture.mdc` — stack, paths, workspaces
2. `.cursor/rules/core.mdc` — TypeScript, React, Tailwind, tests
3. `.cursor/rules/git.mdc` — commits, branches, ignore/cache

Path-scoped rules (`sales-room`, `design-system-figma`, `twenty/*`) win on their globs. Token budget: be concise; no duplicate essays across files.
